code: @Override protected boolean doHandle(CliTerminal terminal, CliSession cliSession, Matcher m, String line) {     try {         cliSession.setFetchSize(Integer.parseInt(m.group(1))).     } catch (NumberFormatException e) {         terminal.line().error("Invalid fetch size [").param(m.group(1)).error("]").end().         return true.     } catch (IllegalArgumentException e) {         terminal.line().error("Invalid fetch size [").param(m.group(1)).error("]. " + e.getMessage()).end().         return true.     }     terminal.line().text("fetch size set to ").em(Integer.toString(cliSession.getFetchSize())).end().     return true. }
